		<title>This Thanksgiving, Make Your Actions Speak Louder than Words with Great Customer Experience</title>
		<link>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/this-thanksgiving-make-your-actions-speak-louder-with-customer-experience.html</link>
				<comments>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/this-thanksgiving-make-your-actions-speak-louder-with-customer-experience.html#respond</comments>
				<pubDate>Thu, 26 Nov 2015 11:58:21 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Alicia Johnson]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Customer Service]]></category>
